  "original_title": "\u0dba\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dda\u0db1\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dbd \u0dba\u0dd4\u0daf \u0dc0\u0dd1\u0dba\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca - \u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Cold War effort based on Ukraine - China",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese State Councilor and Foreign Minister Wang Yi emphasized that he will stand against any attempt to create a new cold war.",
        "Regarding the Ukraine issue, the Chinese minister said:",
        "The two diplomats met in Bali, Indonesia on the sidelines of the G20 Foreign Ministers' Meeting.",
        "Raising China's concerns over the situation in Ukraine, Wang said China opposes the Cold War mentality and any attempt to use the crisis to fuel factional conflict and create a new Cold War.",
        "He said that facing complex and dire challenges, the world values \u200b\u200bcooperation rather than division, and calls for dialogue, not conflict. The Chinese Foreign Minister added that China will continue to firmly stand on the right side of history and promote peace talks."
      ],
